  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">PERU/FLC Sustainable use of vegeyal ivory in 2 natural reserves phase 2</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Alleviating the deforestation pressure in the buffer zones of both Cordillera Escalera Regional Natural Reserve and Cordillera Azul National Park through the promotion of sustainable management of two native palms for the production of vegetal ivory and br
ooms. The communities are already involved in the extraction of non wooden forestry products with good commercial demand which will give them a source of incomes alternative to logging or deforesting for introducing livestock. This phase will allow them to
 start giving added value to their production/ San Martin (North Eastern Amazonia)</narrative>
  </description>
